          <p class='first-para'>
            I have read Birmingham airport's document, but I do not wish to shift the problem to Birmingham. I shall merely say that its airport is not fully utilised at the moment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0392P0_20021105_WH_98'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-tim-boswell' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
