          <p class='first-para'>
            In the interest of saving time, will my hon. Friend accept my complete association, on behalf of all my constituents, with his powerful argument? I would simply add that the behemoth wished upon us would create huge stress on the infrastructure between the midlands and the southeast, and on scarce resources of building and development land.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0392P0_20021105_WH_99'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-andrew-robathan' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0392P0_20021105_WH_99' title='Link to this speech by Mr Andrew Robathan' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
